{"tid":1970784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要對撼「建制」暗藍地區報區議員要主動落區派地區報","createTime":"2020-04-13T11:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T14:29:23.000Z","uid":200663,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0345895bc4464ff39053dc5452cbf153bac08db","tid":1970784,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇睇過呢篇文 未嘅可以睇咗先<br />\n<br />\n（立會）（文宣戰）當你仲沉迷性騷擾緊女手足內鬥果陣 建制選舉機器已經啟動搶攻 新界西出現暗藍地區報 就快連文宣戰都輸埋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1965224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1965224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n其實有唔同手足都已經做緊嘢<br />\n<br />\n至少 馬鞍山 同 葵青 都已經有地區報<br />\n<br />\n反而要做嘅嘢就係要 spread 開去<br />\n<br />\n依家啲地區報接觸面太少喇<br />\n<br />\n我都係去樓下某間黃店先見到自己區嘅區報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以學暗藍地區報咁 區議員落區派報紙<br />\n<br />\n效果會好好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至可以請手足幫手派 保就業 惠民生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地區報其實十分有用<br />\n<br />\n除咗用嚟 SPREAD 區內資訊外<br />\n<br />\n仲可以用嚟做文宣<br />\n<br />\n如果放篇牆紙落去 感染班阿公阿婆<br />\n<br />\n做文宣都易啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果冇地區報嘅地區 強烈建議做一份出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗可以做文宣 仲可以幫手足就業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7d0453417ddeb55fe4d5c2ad47aa5d9f76d8cf","tid":1970784,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"咁快畀人負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6108adb216b3c7180e130d6f3db694609b83f05","tid":1970784,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"Good ar ching"},{"pid":"8e693260edb048a86edcebb5924e3a65a69ba265","tid":1970784,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:02: